scripts.comment: Refer to the TurtleStitch manual cards available on the website, to get this code explained step by step.

block.comment: We have defined a variable named "nr_stitches". Initially it is set to "1". This variable will define the number of stitches per line: the first line will be the lentgh of just 1 stitch.
within the "repeat block" the variable will change by 1 regularly. This will let the triangle grow.
